					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">&quot;1011&quot; isn't necessarily right, the first 10 is fine since it indicates that it wants the nametables rather than the pattern tables, but the &quot;11&quot; afterwards is actually two nametable selection bits, which are part of V.  It could be 00, 01, 10, 11, etc.<br />Aside from that, check that the coarse X is incremented correctly.</div>

					
