				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">T is the &quot;scroll&quot; setting.<br /><br />T is used to automatically reload V at the top of the screen to start drawing the new frame with the desired scroll.<br /><br />It also partially reloads V at the end of every line, just the horizontal bits, again to keep the desired scroll position.</div>

